OL,3,CMan accused of posting offensive
OL,4,Cmaterial online has case dropped
OL,6,FA man accused of posting racially
OL,7,Foffensive material on Facebook amid
OL,8,Fcivil unrest and riots across the UK
OL,9,Fhas had the criminal case against him
OL,10,Fdropped.
OL,12,FGerard Glaister, 56, was charged early
OL,13,Flast month as Cumbria police took
OL,14,Faction and put tough measures in place
OL,15,Fafter reports circulated online of
OL,16,Fpotential planned disorder in the
OL,17,Fcounty.
OL,19,FMr Glaister had faced one charge
OL,20,Fbrought under the Malicious
OL,21,FCommunications Act 1988.
