OL,3,CMan accused of posting offensive
OL,4,Cmaterial online has case dropped
OL,6,FThis alleged that he had displayed `
OL,7,Fon his Facebook page ` content which
OL,8,Fcourt papers said was "of an indecent
OL,9,For grossly offensive nature for the
OL,10,Fpurpose of causing distress or
OL,11,Fanxiety".
OL,13,FMr Glaister, from Workington, appeared
OL,14,Fat Carlisle Crown Court on Friday 13
OL,15,FSeptember.
