OL,6,F"You will understand that posting
OL,7,Fmaterial on the internet, whether that
OL,8,Fis on your social media or your
OL,9,Fplatforms can ` and does ` constitute
OL,10,Fcriminal offences and can have serious
OL,11,Frepercussions, and you should take
OL,12,Fgreat care in future."
OL,14,FMr Glaister had his licence to drive a
OL,15,Ftaxi taken off him by Cumberland
OL,16,FCouncil after he was charged. He told
OL,17,FITV Border he will try to get it back.
