OL,6,FA statement from Cumberland Council
OL,7,Fsaid: "Following the Crown Prosecution
OL,8,FServices' decision to discontinue Mr
OL,9,FGlaister's charges, he will now have
OL,10,Fthe opportunity to reapply for his
OL,11,Fhackney carriage driver licence.
OL,13,F"His application will be put before
OL,14,Four licensing Regulatory Sub-Committee
OL,15,Fin due course."
OL,17,FMegan Morrison, aged 26, of Mona Road,
OL,18,FSalterbeck, also appeared at the crown
OL,19,Fcourt today.
