OL,6,FShe faces a charge which alleges that
OL,7,Fshe "published written material on
OL,8,FFacebook which was threatening,
OL,9,Fabusive or insulting with the intent
OL,10,Fthereby to stir up racial hatred".
OL,12,FNo plea has yet been entered by
OL,13,FMorrison. Her case was adjourned and a
OL,14,Ftrial date has previously been set for
OL,15,F15th January.
OL,17,FDerek Heggie, aged 40, of Welsh Road,
OL,18,FCarlisle, was due to attend Carlisle
OL,19,FCrown Court remotely over a video link
OL,20,Fthis afternoon.
