OL,6,FHe is alleged to have posted racially
OL,7,Faggravated comments on a YouTube
OL,8,Fpodcast between 3-7 August.
OL,10,FHe did not attend court due to an
OL,11,Fadministrative error, and his case was
OL,12,Fadjourned until Wednesday of next
OL,13,Fweek. A trial date of 2 December has
OL,14,Falready been set.
